                    },
                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "You display  *The Fool* to your foes in a clumsy, awkward, and embarrassing way. Choose up to four creatures within 60 feet. These four creatures must attempt a Will save against your class DC.",
                    "critical_success": "The creature is unaffected.",
                    "success": "The creature is distracted by your antics and is stupefied 1 until the start of your next turn.",
                    "failure": "The creature is stupefied 2.",
                    "critical_failure": "The creature is stupefied 3. In addition, for 1 minute, the creature is confused .",
